song 🌿 olivia (threat) 16-Sep-22 09:15 PM
It doesn't take much time for you to find information on both you client and her playmates. Lang Xin is quick to point out his involvement on the case five years prior - his hit role as the "sidekick". Information on his partner-in-crime, Feihong Hu, follows shortly. Currently employed at the MCPD, he may or may not have information for you. Context for the upcoming play, if you will. Your "ally" (you suppose that's what he is, yes), awaits you in a side room - away from the frantic bustle of the rest of the department. It's a humble room, equipped with a table and chairs. A person sits, facing you as you enter, papers and files spread in an array in front of him. He looks minutely pissed. You suppose anyone would be, after reading that mockery of a note.
